cs.GT, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.LG

The paper deals with the study of pacing equilibria in ad auctions, which involves game theory (cs.GT) and optimization (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the efficient computability of the solution concept, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The topic of ad auctions is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and market analysis (cs.MA).
